metadata.name: TWO TEN GOD
metadata.description: TRIPLETS is an exploration of semiotics and pseudonymity on the blockchain. You are TWO TEN GOD and TWO TEN GOD is you. Use it to build your personal brand in the metaverse; your alter ego is unique to you and it is yours now. To see if it's available as an ENS name, check https://app.ens.domains/search/TWOTENGOD. Twitter handle? https://twitter.com/TWOTENGOD. Now go forth and build.
